<p>Hello <%= @resource.first_name %>!</p>

<p>The captain of the "<%= @resource.team.name %>" has invited you to join their <%= @resource.team.sport.downcase %> team on Huddl, you can accept it by clicking <%= link_to "here", accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @token) %>.

<% if @resource.invitation_due_at %>
  Please note this invitation will expire <%= @resource.invitation_due_at.strftime('%b %eth, %Y') %>.</p>
<% else %>
  </p>
<% end %>

<p>If you don't want to accept the invitation, just ignore this email. Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your password.</p>

-Huddl
